{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_17","type":"agent_message","text":"The environment has both `OPENAI_API_KEY` and `OPENROUTER_KEY`, so the implementation can call real hosted models. I’m leaning toward a compact controlled study on QMSum/GovReport-style texts plus LLM-as-judge error typing, because it directly estimates error slopes by length without requiring fragile local factuality checkpoints."}}
